					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Curse you Sir Baubius! (but thanks for the comment)</p> <p>So this was initially inspired by <a href="https://i.redd.it/ls6jo7tx4mzz.jpg">this</a>, itself connected to 049-J, though the idea evolved significantly from there and it mostly became a backstory for Darke, or my <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/so-they-called-him-darke">Darke</a> anyway.</p> <p>As usual with my scips, I don't feel this quite reached its full potential, but my feedback was starting to go in circles so I guess it's as good as I can make it.</p> <p>Thanks to everyone on chat and the forums who gave me advice on this.</p> 
				 	]]>
